2026-04-29T05:58:46.7294916Z 13    <!--
2026-04-29T05:58:46.7295853Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-29T05:58:46.7296753Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-29T05:58:46.7298003Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-29T05:58:46.7298949Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-29T05:58:46.7300278Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
